name: ProceduresSnomedCtIpsFreeSet
title: Procedures - SNOMED CT IPS Free Set

description: This value set includes the codes from the SNOMED International Patient Set (IPS) subset of SNOMED CT (IPS Free Set) that are included in: descendants of 71388002 \|Procedure (procedure)\|, but excludes descendants of 14734007 \|Administrative procedure (procedure)\|, 59524001 \|Blood bank procedure (procedure)\|, 389067005 \|Community health procedure (procedure)\|, 442006003 \|Determination of information related to transfusion (procedure)\|, 225288009 \|Environmental care procedure (procedure)\|, 308335008 \|Patient encounter procedure (procedure)\|, 710135002 \|Promotion (procedure)\|, and 389084004 \|Staff related procedure (procedure)\|.
